S:log-item.D:comment: Enhance ManifestHeaderProcessor to support Provide-Capability and Require-Capability style headers. The functionality can be found in: ManifestHeaderProcessor.parseCapabilityString() ManifestHeaderProcessor.parseRequirementString() Currently the implementation of both is exactly the same under the hood, but I introduced them as separate methods to make make usage feel more naturally. It will also allow fixes to them individually in the future if needed.
